Mailgun API wrapper for Ruby

Documentation:
=============
Please visit our documentation page at 
http://documentation.mailgun.net


Installation
============

* Make sure you have ActiveResource gem installed
* Download mailgun.rb file

Getting started:
================

require 'mailgun.rb'

Mailgun::init("my-api-key", "https://mailgun.net/api")
Mailbox.find(:all).each do |mbox|
    puts mbox.id
end

For more visit http://documentation.mailgun.net

--
MG team
